import GridSystem from './GridSystem.js';

                currentId : 0

    render() {
        return (

            <>

                <GridSystem colCount={5}>          
                    {this.state.conection}                                             
                </GridSystem>

                
                <DrawArrows>
                    {this.state.conection}
                </DrawArrows>
                
            </>
        )
    }
}

export default ViewerNetworkVisualization
